{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/splinter-cell-hadir-di-ghost-recon/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mata-mata Super Splinter Cell Kembali Hadir Di Game Ghost Recon","content":"<p>Masih ingat dengan game Splinter Cell? Buat kamu yang sempat menggilai game Java atau Symbian di Nokia, game yang satu ini nggak boleh ketinggalan di dalam setiap ponsel. Bermain sebagai agen rahasia Sam Fisher, kamu harus menyelesaikan setiap level tanpa tertangkap oleh musuh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45746\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45746\" data-attachment-id=\"45746\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/splinter-cell-hadir-di-ghost-recon/attachment/01-splinter-cell/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-splinter-cell\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45746\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell.jpg\" alt=\"01-splinter-cell\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45746\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Fresh Wallpapers</p></div></p>\n<p>Splinter Cell merupakan game produksi Ubisoft, yang mana hak produksi game ponselnya diberikan kepada anak perusahaannya, Gameloft. Setiap kali ada game Splinter Cell baru yang dibuat Ubisoft, Gameloft selalu membuat game versi ponselnya.</p>\n<p>Sejak 2013, tidak ada game Splinter Cell baru lain selain Splinter Cell Blacklist. Namun, kini agen Sam Fisher akan kembali terjun ke medan perang mengenakan seragam dan teropong malam ikoniknya. Sosok Sam kini hadir di game saudaranya, Ghost Recon.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45747\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45747\" data-attachment-id=\"45747\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/splinter-cell-hadir-di-ghost-recon/attachment/02-splinter-cell/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-splinter-cell\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45747\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell.jpg\" alt=\"02-splinter-cell\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45747\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ScreenRant</p></div></p>\n<p>Sam Fisher bakal menjadi karakter utama dalam <em>update</em> game <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tak-hanya-pubg-dan-fortnite-game-berikut-juga-cocok-untuk-mode-battle-royale-death-match/\">Ghost Recon: Wildlands</a> terbaru, yakni Special Operation 1: Splinter Cell. Dalam <em>update</em> ini, kamu bisa memainkan misi PvE terbaru bersama sang agen rahasia. Diceritakan bahwa seseorang telah mencuri data rahasia dari CIA dan menjualnya ke kartel narkoba Santa Blanca. Sam Fisher diterjunkan ke Bolivia untuk mengambil data tersebut. Pasukan khusus Ghost pun ditunjuk sebagai bala bantuan Sam.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HRmQhlVQpLI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Dalam misi PvE ini, <em>stealth</em> menjadi kunci penting. Layaknya game Splinter Cell, kamu harus menyelesaikan misi tanpa ditemukan oleh penjaga musuh. Berita baiknya, kamu menjalankan misi tersebut di malam hari. Namun jangan harap penjagaan musuh akan lebih kendor dari siang hari.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45748\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45748\" data-attachment-id=\"45748\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/splinter-cell-hadir-di-ghost-recon/attachment/03-splinter-cell/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-splinter-cell\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45748\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell.jpg\" alt=\"03-splinter-cell\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45748\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Eurogamer</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan menyelesaikan misi ini, kamu akan mendapatkan hadiah teropong malam milik Sam, ranjau pendeteksi jarak, dan <em>emblem</em> Splinter Cell. Selain itu, ada juga <em>equipment pack</em> berisi senapan SC-4000 milik Sam, <em>skin</em> pistol Five-Seven, pisau kerambit, kostum dan teropong malam Sam, sarung tangan Echelon, serta 3 <em>skin</em> senjata baru.</p>\n<p><em>Update</em> ini juga akan diterapkan ke mode PvP dari Ghost Recon: Wildlands, yakni Ghost War. Terdapat <em>map</em> baru, mode game baru, serta <em>class</em> baru bernama Echelon. <em>Class</em> Echelon memiliki kemampuan yang sama seperti Sam Fisher, sehingga ia mampu menyergap musuh tanpa diketahui.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45749\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45749\" data-attachment-id=\"45749\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/splinter-cell-hadir-di-ghost-recon/attachment/04-splinter-cell/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-splinter-cell\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45749 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell.jpg\" alt=\"04 splinter cell\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-splinter-cell-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45749\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Donâ€™t Feed The Gamers</p></div></p>\n<p>Rilisnya <em>update</em> terbaru untuk Ghost Recon: Wildlands ini bukannya tanpa alasan. Konon Ubisoft menyiapkan <em>update</em> ini sebagai <em>teaser</em> untuk game Splinter Cell terbaru yang bakal diungkap di E3 2018 nanti. Benar atau nggaknya, sepertinya kita masih harus menunggu informasi yang bisa dipercaya. Untuk saat ini, nggak ada salahnya bernostalgia bersama mata-mata super Sam Fisher di dalam dunia Ghost Recon!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"766048d2-dd00-5a5e-a9c6-2b96a6d9daa7"}}}